title.rendered: Asset Round Poseur Table – Laminate Top

content.rendered:
Our Asset Dining Table Range is made with a Steel & Chrome base & column and a laminate table top. Shown in a round Beech laminate top.

Available in 5 standard laminates and a choice of sizes so that your tables suit your needs & requirements to the fullest possibility.  

The Asset table range comes with:

  • Height adjustable feet
  • Cast Iron Base & Column
  • 25mm thick TuffTop with an MDF core
  • Matching 2mm ABS edge to protect the table top
  • Our laminate tops can withstand up to 180 degrees centigrade, meaning no need for linen or table mats. 
  • Laminate tops can also withstand harsh cleaning products, such as antibacterial cleaner

These items come with a 1 year guarantee. Held in stock for delivery in 3-4 working days.

We work with a number of laminate suppliers so you can customise your table, to suit you.

This item requires basic self assembly. **SCREWS ARE NOT INCLUDED AS STANDARD ON THIS PRODUCT – AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST, FREE OF CHARGE**
